Description: Implements various Riemannian metrics for symmetric positive definite matrices, including AIRM (Affine Invariant Riemannian Metric), Log-Euclidean, Euclidean, Log-Cholesky, and Bures-Wasserstein metrics. Provides functions for computing logarithmic and exponential maps, vectorization, and statistical operations on the manifold of positive definite matrices.
